{"tid":1322684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【釋出善意】請各位香港人同情黑警，切勿殺狗，只許殘廢，或綁於燈柱唾虐，令其終身遺憾出賣香港","createTime":"2019-07-16T04:18:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T07:15:35.000Z","uid":131691,"like":74,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"b6768f58e612948d2af2a139cb772b1158f04195","tid":1322684,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:18:57.000Z","msg":"對於賣港奴，死亡是優待<br />\n而且港共有安家費<br />\n不值得<br />\n<br />\n但必須侮辱<br />\n要麼打擊警隊士氣，令其潰不成軍<br />\n要麼逼狗埋牆，引發緊嚴重失誤，續發攬炒<br />\n<br />\n歷史上，有以下記載：<br />\n身上留下出賣的印記<br />\n綁在公眾位置<br />\n戲謔<br />\n或甚至令其殘廢<br />\n<br />\n裝備：<br />\n麻繩/尼龍繩<br />\nMarker pen<br />\n自由發揮<br />\n<br />\nStory time:<br />\n英國古時長弓兵能於遠處殺死無數法國重騎兵<br />\n因此若有英國弓兵被捕，會切斷拉弓用的手指<br />\n同時，當遇上法國騎兵時，英國弓兵會展示倒轉的V字手勢，以示挑釁。"},{"pid":"4ad1badb18733dd7f9d9bc94ae165849e0df614b","tid":1322684,"uid":124859,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:19:42.000Z","msg":"昨日我都開post講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8d69f18abd114d9f305902f49890ff5fc4f997a","tid":1322684,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ad1badb18733dd7f9d9bc94ae165849e0df614b","tid":1322684,"uid":124859,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:19:42.000Z","msg":"昨日我都開post講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:21:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"930006df26d332e5083985614ed259c4a9c0e16d","tid":1322684,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8d69f18abd114d9f305902f49890ff5fc4f997a","tid":1322684,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ad1badb18733dd7f9d9bc94ae165849e0df614b","tid":1322684,"uid":124859,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:19:42.000Z","msg":"昨日我都開post講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:21:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:21:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"528d6b9937570bd8be0b1fe82b1c9d33a3cf8122","tid":1322684,"uid":102343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:22:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打機咁，等對家全部中哂控場，自己人推塔都方便d。<br />\n<br />\n另外，歡迎比下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇熟IT嘅巴打整番個網上立法會?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1322535\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1322535</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"88215b7ed5a11c1b8c99419c7721098c6e3dd3f2","tid":1322684,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:23:31.000Z","msg":"認同，殘廢係最恰到好處既做法"},{"pid":"f4a4afc0c999a463aa96deb0d25e9f9d089a1dae","tid":1322684,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:26:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你覺得孫子兵法有冇邊段值得參考，我覺得前線走位方法要有啲共同知識"},{"pid":"e373e2cc1196e85a90893593816ffa9fabe60784","tid":1322684,"uid":22116,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:27:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家記住</span><br />\n死狗只會激勵對方士氣 光明正大鎮壓<br />\n踢幾下 佢轉頭返去沖個涼 換完更 聽日又出黎打過<br />\n但如果骨折斷手腳 就幾年甚至終生都做唔返狗 佢對支共黎講就係棄子 分分鐘共產黨會安排佢被自殺黎激勵士氣"},{"pid":"4d67dfa3b629cd6b8fb91b6f1d5f60d5e416af81","tid":1322684,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:28:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n提防運動失焦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b61d4b26e25d317a502e365a3c3b8374cd9eaa48","tid":1322684,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:30:00.000Z","msg"